  </div>
  </section>
    <section class="main-section" id="golf">  
<header>Golf</header>        
<p>Golf is a great solo-playing sport. It is one of the most recreational sports. Golf was first played in the Kingdom of Scotland.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Tiger Woods is regarded as the best golfer of all time.</li>
